n the Middle Ages in England, but fell out of favour in the 16th century until it was revived in the 20th century. Little Hugh of Lincoln was a child supposed in the Middle Ages to have been murdered by Jews in about  1255 , a legend responsible for several outbursts of anti-Semitism at various times. The story is referred to by  Chaucer  in The Prioress's Tale. He is not to be confused with  St Hugh of Lincoln  (  1140–1200 ), bishop of Lincoln (  1186–1200 ), who was noted for his charity and good works, his piety, and his defence of the Church against the State. Since the later Middle Ages <i>Hugh</i> has also been used as an Anglicized form of the Gaelic name Aodh ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Hugh Preston was born about 1372, in England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter. He died in his hometown."},"et":{"aproximadamente 1372–":"umbes 1372–Surnud","1397–Female":"1397–Surnud","1372–Male":"1372–Surnud","aproximadamente 1372":"umbes 1372","1397":"1397","1372":"1372","Inglaterra, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"aproximadamente 1372–":"noin 1372–Kuollut","1397–Female":"1397–Kuollut","1372–Male":"1372–Kuollut","aproximadamente 1372":"noin 1372","1397":"1397","1372":"1372","Inglaterra, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"aproximadamente 1372–":"environ 1372–Décédé","1397–Female":"1397–Décédée","1372–Male":"1372–Décédé","aproximadamente 1372":"environ 1372","1397":"1397","1372":"1372","Inglaterra, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Hugh Preston est né environ 1372, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"aproximadamente 1372–":"um 1372–Verstorben","1397–Female":"1397–Verstorben","1372–Male":"1372–Verstorben","aproximadamente 1372":"um 1372","1397":"1397","1372":"1372","Inglaterra, United Kingdom":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Hugh Preston wurde um 1372 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter. Er 